title: Delhi High Court orders Indiabulls housing finance to reconcile project loan accounts of Supertech - Economic Times
content: Delhi High Court orders Indiabulls housing finance to reconcile project loan accounts of Supertech  Economic Times
description: Realty developer has alleged that they have paid extra amount to Indiabulls and want to financial institution to return the amount and clear the project so that homebuyers can get the flat registered.
